node.text:
First attempt with the "Roll Up Crispy Bacon with Bread and Smashed Eggs"
.
I think I can do it better than this as I run out of mayonnaise which the eggs are not that creamy. I should have added more shredded cheese too. Will try it again.
.
#sgbreakfast #homecook #breakfastidea #stayhome #circuitbreakersg #circuitbreakerextended #mightyhomecook
@kei_camui is it? I have not try it before. Let me check it out 😋
Reminds me of PB's sweet bacon roll~~
@foodgemsg Yes Mei, going to do better next time. Stay safe and catch up with u next month.
@justjiahui haha, it will be more shiok if the eggs is mixed with mayonnaise
@mightyfoodie next time u try again haha. More flavourful right
@mummyprissy I pan fry it but maybe next time I will try airfly it
So you pan fry it or bake?
@instabetha luego dice que lo fríe a la sartén... que tal quedará horneado?
